column99:
Main responsibility will be: 
 
 Communication with Suppliers & Travel Agents in Asia and handling all kinds of agents’ requests with a problem solving, professional attitude 
 Management of all pre & post-booking enquiries from customers or Travel Agents 
 Creation of tour quotations upon specific needs 
 Contract management (with suppliers and customers). Communicate with both aiming and based on profitable conditions. 
 Handling crisis/emergency situations in regards to their groups 
 Management and maintenance of an existing customer portfolio 
 Correct and accurate usage of company’s tools and business processes 
 
   
 Profile Required: 
 
 Fluent in English / Korean & Chinese knowledge is a plus 
 Advanced Excel user - Excellent keyboard skills 
 Good time management skills with excellent attention to detail. Timely and accurate processing of orders 
 Preferably, at least 1-2 years of relevant experience in Tourism industry
